quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,96,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, Àjọkẹ́-ayé yóò fi ìfẹ́ sáààrin wọn.",""
  19,97,"Nítorí náà, dájúdájú A fi èdè abínibí rẹ (èdè Lárúbáwá) ṣe (kíké al-Ƙur’ān àti àgbọ́yé rẹ̀) ní ìrọ̀rùn nítorí kí o lè fi ṣe ìró ìdùnnú fún àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) àti nítorí kí o lè fi ṣe ìkìlọ̀ fún ìjọ tó ń ja òdodo níyàn",""
  19,98,"Mélòó mélòó nínú ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn! Ǹjẹ́ o gbọ́ ìró ẹnì kan kan nínú wọn mọ́ tàbí (ǹjẹ́) o gbọ́ ohùn kẹ́lẹ́kẹ́lẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ wọn bí?",""
  20,1,"Tọ̄ hā. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  20,2,"A kò sọ al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ fún ọ láti kó wàhálà bá ọ.",""
  20,3,"Bí kò ṣe pé ó jẹ́ ìrántí fún ẹni tó ń páyà (Allāhu).",""
  20,4,"(Ó jẹ́) ìmísí tó sọ̀kalẹ̀ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Ẹni tí Ó dá ilẹ̀ àti àwọn sánmọ̀ gíga.",""
  20,5,"Àjọkẹ́-ayé gúnwà sórí Ìtẹ́-ọlá.",""
  20,6,"TiRẹ̀ ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀, ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà láààrin méjèèjì àti ohunkóhun tó wà lábẹ́ ilẹ̀.",""
  20,7,"Tí o bá sọ ọ̀rọ̀ jáde, dájúdájú (Allāhu) mọ ìkọ̀kọ̀ àti ohun tí ó (tún) pamọ́ jùlọ.",""
  20,8,"Allāhu, kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. TiRẹ̀ ni àwọn orúkọ tó dára jùlọ.",""
  20,9,"Ǹjẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (Ànábì) Mūsā dé ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ?",""
  20,10,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó rí iná kan, ó sọ fún àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ pé: “Ẹ dúró síbí. Dájúdájú èmi rí iná kan. Ó ṣeé ṣe kí n̄g rí ògúnná mú wá fún yín nínú rẹ̀ tàbí kí n̄g rí ojú ọ̀nà kan nítòsí iná náà.”",""
  20,11,"Nígbà tí ó dé ibẹ̀, A pè é “Mūsā,",""
  20,12,"Dájúdájú Èmi ni Olúwa rẹ. Nítorí náà, bọ́ bàtà rẹ méjèèjì sílẹ̀.<sup>1</sup> Dájúdájú ìwọ wà ní àfonífojì mímọ́, Tuwā.","[1] Ìdí tí Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - fi pa á láṣẹ fún Ànábì Mūsā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - láti bọ́ bàtà ẹsẹ̀ rẹ̀ sílẹ̀, gẹ́gẹ́ bí ọmọ Mọs‘ūd - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí i - ṣe gbà á wá ni pé, awọ òkúǹbete kẹ́tẹ́kẹ́tẹ́ tí wọn kò pa lósè ni wọ́n fi ṣe bàtà náà."
